            <h4 style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;">Thông tin liên hệ</h4>

            <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt" style="margin-right: 8px; color: #dc3545;"></i>
