            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <i class="fas fa-envelope" style="margin-right: 8px; color: #007bff;"></i>
                <a href="mailto:jeanruych@gmail.com" style="text-decoration: none; color: #333;">jeanruych@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <i class="fas fa-phone" style="margin-right: 8px; color: #28a745;"></i>
                <a href="tel:0379034609" style="text-decoration: none; color: #333;">0379 034 609</a>
            </p>

            <div>
